{
  "title": "Linux上删除空行的方法",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h2 class=\"title\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;\">Linux上删除空行的方法</h2><div class=\"meta\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"info\">一 11th, 2014\t</div><div class=\"comments\">151 views | \t<a href=\"http://smilejay.com/2014/01/linux-delete-blank-line/#respond\">发表评论</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://smilejay.com/2014/01/linux-delete-blank-line/trackback/\" rel=\"trackback\">Trackback</a></div></div><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">在Linux上处理一些数据文件时，有时候需要将其中的空行过滤掉，系统中提供的各种工具都可以完成这个功能。将常用的介绍如下吧：<br>1. grep</p><div class=\"wp_codebox_msgheader\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"right\"></span><span class=\"left\"><a>View Code</a>&nbsp;BASH</span></div><div class=\"wp_codebox\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><table><tbody><tr id=\"p20811\"><td class=\"line_numbers\"><pre>1\n2\n3\n</pre></td><td class=\"code\" id=\"p2081code1\"><pre class=\"bash\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">grep</span> . data.txt\n<span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">grep</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 0, 51);\">-v</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'^$'</span> data.txt\n<span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">grep</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'[^$]'</span> data.txt</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">2. sed</p><div class=\"wp_codebox_msgheader\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"right\"></span><span class=\"left\"><a>View Code</a>&nbsp;BASH</span></div><div class=\"wp_codebox\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><table><tbody><tr id=\"p20812\"><td class=\"line_numbers\"><pre>1\n2\n3\n</pre></td><td class=\"code\" id=\"p2081code2\"><pre class=\"bash\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">sed</span>  <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'/^$/d'</span> data.txt\n<span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">sed</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'/^\\s*$/d'</span> data.txt   <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: italic;\">#这个命令还可将完全空格、tab等组成的空行删掉。</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: italic;\"># The character class \\s will match the whitespace characters &lt;tab&gt; and &lt;space&gt;.</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">3. awk</p><div class=\"wp_codebox_msgheader\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"right\"></span><span class=\"left\"><a>View Code</a>&nbsp;BASH</span></div><div class=\"wp_codebox\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><table><tbody><tr id=\"p20813\"><td class=\"line_numbers\"><pre>1\n2\n</pre></td><td class=\"code\" id=\"p2081code3\"><pre class=\"bash\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">awk</span> NF data.txt   <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: italic;\"># 这个也可以将空格、tab等组成的空行删掉。</span>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">awk</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'!/^$/'</span> data.txt</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">4. tr</p><div class=\"wp_codebox_msgheader\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"right\"></span><span class=\"left\"><a>View Code</a>&nbsp;BASH</span></div><div class=\"wp_codebox\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><table><tbody><tr id=\"p20814\"><td class=\"line_numbers\"><pre>1\n</pre></td><td class=\"code\" id=\"p2081code4\"><pre class=\"bash\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 12, 185); font-weight: bold;\">tr</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 0, 51);\">-s</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">'\\n'</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;\">&lt;</span> data.txt</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">貌似这些可以处理的命令里面，“grep . data.txt”这个的效率是比较高的；如果处理大数据量时可以比较一些这些命令的性能。</p>"
    }
  ]
